Cavity_CycleSetDownloadAndGoDownloadGoGe: Limits cycle temperatures to 135F to help protect items prone to melting with varying soil levels.  If selected, Heat Dry is also shortened to limit heat input.
Cavity_CycleSetDownloadAndGoDownloadGoHe: Provides extra wash time and heat to clean tougher items with baked-on food residue.
Cavity_CycleSetDownloadAndGoDownloadGoQu: Quick cleaning power. Perfect for cleaning food prep items (such as mixing bowls) and getting everything ready for an event.
Cavity_CycleSetDownloadAndGoDownloadGoSa: Uses extra wash time and high temperatures (156F) to ensure important items come out clean.
Cavity_CycleSetDownloadAndGoDownloadGoSp: Senses the amount of wash time and heat needed to clean food residue. Great for items that may need a little more care.
Cavity_CycleSetOptionUpperRackOnly.Descr: Washes dishes on the top rack only. Can be used with any wash cycle.
Cavity_CycleSetOptionLowerRackOnly.Descr: Washes dishes on the bottom rack only. Can be used with any wash cycle.
Cavity_CycleSetOptionSaniRinse.Descripti: The final rinse water is heated to 155°F (68.3°C), eliminating 99.999% of food soil bacteria.
Cavity_CycleSetOptionSmartHeatedDry.Desc: Active drying that evenly dries with heat and a fan.
Cavity_CycleSetOptionBottleWashZone.Desc: Articulating nozzles deliver a high-powered spray into tall items, including vases and champagne flutes.
Cavity_CycleSetOptionSteam.Description: Helps your stemware glisten by generating a cloud of steam before the final rinse cycle.
Cavity_CycleSetOptionHighTemp.Descriptio: Provides increased water temperature during washing for hard-to-remove soils.

Notifications.Label: Notifications
Notifications.Description: Commencer ou arrêter de recevoir des notifications en tout temps
SabbathMode.Label: Sabbath mode
SabbathMode.Description: Permet au lave-vaisselle d'agir conformément aux directives religieuses en vigueur pendant le sabbat et les fêtes religieuses
QuietMode.Label: Quiet mode
QuietMode.Description: Met au silence les tonalités lors de l’appui sur les boutons du tableau de commande et empêche le signal du programme terminé
